definitions.definition: An exercise session ; a period of physical exercise.
A schedule or program of specific exercises , especially one intended to achieve a particular goal .
Any activity that requires much physical or mental effort , or produces strain .

main_definition: An exercise session ; a period of physical exercise.
secondary_definitions: A schedule or program of specific exercises , especially one intended to achieve a particular goal .
( by extension ) Any activity that requires much physical or mental effort , or produces strain .
